Effective with the last binary compatible 1.x releases, apr-util becomes part
of apr itself.  To find version 2.0 apr-util functionality see;

  http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/apr/apr/trunk

  http://svn.apache.org/viewvc/apr/apr/trunk (ViewCV browsable interface)

use -1, because it might put it on the wire as an unsigned int.

We previously special-cased this for the MSSDK, but it needs to be more general.
